95
00:03:56,840 --> 00:04:02,940
Wow. Bigger Brother's clothes are funny.

96
00:04:02,940 --> 00:04:04,220
Aren't they heavy?

97
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:08,800
It's all right. 
Big Brother is very strong.

98
00:04:13,850 --> 00:04:18,730
I'm sure you'll have a chance to 
discuss their natures at some point.

99
00:04:19,340 --> 00:04:20,950
Until you do, just accept them.

100
00:04:22,620 --> 00:04:25,490
Okay, Nina, go play outside.

101
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:29,790
Alexander must be lonesome.

102
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,830
Okay then, I'll see you later.

103
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:42,220
Who would have thought you'd aspire to be State Alchemists at your ages?

104
00:04:44,080 --> 00:04:47,380
If there's anything I can do for you, 
just let me know, okay?

105
00:04:47,380 --> 00:04:52,000
Well, Tucker-san, I'd like to have you 
show us the Chimera you transmuted.

106
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:52,640
Me too.

107
00:04:55,140 --> 00:04:59,350
Oh, it died not long after 
it was transmuted, you see...

108
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:03,580
Anyways, passing marks come first.

109
00:05:03,580 --> 00:05:06,660
It will take more than just an 
overnight effort to pass this test.

110
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:15,160
This is the materials room. You're free to use it.

111
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:19,170
This is incredible, Brother. 
It's full of books I've never even seen!

112
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:21,350
The materials in here are just a fraction

113
